name: The Lil Horror’s Moonlight Stroll
description:
7444px x 6000px 300dpi PNG

Strolling along a bright moonlit evening are the Lil Horrors, an intrepid gang of spooks hailing from the land of Salem in dimension 66F where they get up to mischief. The leader of the gang, Manny is known for his jovial nature and has a penchant	 for unstoppable dancing when ever he hears the right tune. Jackie the Lantern was born from hell fire and inhabits a cursed pumpkin, he’s known for his pranks. Blair the Void Witch comes from another dimension and is overly excited at seemingly everything. Ludvig the Vegan Vampr is the son of a famous Nosferatu but has chosen to only feed on plants and vegetables, particularly the green variety. Selina is a servant of the Cat Goddess Bastet and hangs out with the gang out of amusement and boredom. Boris the bandaged is a loveable giant who’s never revealed what’s under all of his wrappings. Lastly we have Doc, a mysterious scientist who wandered into Dimension 66F after conducting strange experiments, no one can understand a word they say under their mask. 

#HenHalloween
